OL,3,CBlind voters say they're still
OL,4,Cstruggling to cast their ballot
OL,5,Cprivately
OL,7,FVisually impaired people in our region
OL,8,Fsay they're still struggling to cast
OL,9,Ftheir ballot privately.
OL,11,FIn the last General Election, only 13
OL,12,Fper cent of those registered blind
OL,13,Fcould vote independently and in secret
OL,14,Faccording to the Royal National
OL,15,FInstitute of Blind (RNIB).
OL,17,FEdward Bebbington has muscular
OL,18,Fdegeneration which left him partially
OL,19,Fsighted twenty years ago.
