OL,7,FEdward's wife helps him with the
OL,8,Fvoting process but says more needs to
OL,9,Fbe done to make voting accessible for
OL,10,Fall.
OL,12,FHe said: "I do find it frustrating
OL,13,Fbecause the philosophy we have in this
OL,14,Fcountry, and legislation that's been
OL,15,Fpassed, the Equality Act, one
OL,16,Fshouldn't be disadvantaged by one's
OL,17,Fdisability.
OL,19,F"It does make you feel a bit different
OL,20,Fwhen you actually just want to play
OL,21,Fyour part in society.
